"Label" = "標籤";
"Namespace" = "命名空間";
"No Kubernetes contexts configured." = "尚未設定 Kubernetes 內容。";
"No bridged interfaces available. Bromure AC will fall back to NAT at launch." = "沒有可用的橋接介面。Bromure AC 啟動時將回退至 NAT。";
"No other API tokens configured." = "尚未設定其他 API 權杖。";
"Off → nothing recorded. Activity → metadata only (host, status, latency, swap report, leak warnings). AI request details → also captures bodies for known LLM hosts (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Cohere, Mistral, Perplexity, x.ai, Groq, Replicate, HuggingFace). Everything → bodies for every host. Bodies are AES-GCM encrypted with the same keychain key as profile secrets. View at App → Trace Inspector (⇧⌘I)." = "關閉 → 不記錄任何內容。活動 → 僅後設資料（主機、狀態、延遲、替換報告、洩漏警告）。AI 請求詳情 → 同時擷取已知 LLM 主機（Anthropic、OpenAI、Google、Cohere、Mistral、Perplexity、x.ai、Groq、Replicate、HuggingFace）的內容。全部 → 所有主機的內容。內容會使用與設定機密相同的鑰匙圈金鑰進行 AES-GCM 加密。請於 App → Trace Inspector (⇧⌘I) 檢視。";
"Open DigitalOcean token page in your browser" = "在瀏覽器中開啟 DigitalOcean 權杖頁面";
"Open this host's token-creation page in your browser" = "在瀏覽器中開啟此主機的權杖建立頁面";
"Optional. Leave blank to trust the Bromure CA only (the proxy still validates the upstream)." = "選用。留空僅信任 Bromure CA（代理仍會驗證上游）。";
"Passphrase (leave blank if none)" = "密語（若無請留空）";
"Passphrase is in your macOS Keychain." = "密語儲存在您的 macOS 鑰匙圈中。";
"Passphrases (if any) are stored in the macOS Keychain — bromure-ac fetches via SSH_ASKPASS at session launch and never logs the value." = "密語（若有）儲存在 macOS 鑰匙圈中 — bromure-ac 於工作階段啟動時透過 SSH_ASKPASS 取得，絕不會記錄該值。";
"Password / token" = "密碼 / 權杖";
"Paste this into github.com/settings/keys (or your hosting provider's equivalent). The matching private key lives only inside this profile." = "將此貼上至 github.com/settings/keys（或您的服務供應商對應頁面）。對應的私鑰只存在於此設定中。";
"Personal access token from cloud.digitalocean.com → API → Generate New Token. Injected into the VM as `DIGITALOCEAN_ACCESS_TOKEN` env + `~/.config/doctl/config.yaml` — `doctl auth init` is unnecessary, you're already logged in." = "來自 cloud.digitalocean.com → API → Generate New Token 的個人存取權杖。會以 `DIGITALOCEAN_ACCESS_TOKEN` 環境變數加上 `~/.config/doctl/config.yaml` 注入到虛擬機中 — 無需執行 `doctl auth init`，您已登入。";
"Personal access tokens for git over HTTPS. Stored encrypted on the host; the proxy swaps them onto outbound requests so the VM only ever holds the fake. `gh` and `glab` pick up GH_TOKEN / GITLAB_TOKEN env automatically." = "用於 HTTPS git 的個人存取權杖。在主機上加密保存；代理會在傳出請求時進行替換，因此虛擬機僅持有假權杖。`gh` 與 `glab` 會自動讀取 GH_TOKEN / GITLAB_TOKEN 環境變數。";
"Point bromure at any existing SSH private key (RSA, ed25519, ecdsa) — encrypted ones included. The key is loaded into the per-profile bromure ssh-agent at every session launch; passphrases are stored in the macOS Keychain." = "將 bromure 指向任何現有的 SSH 私鑰（RSA、ed25519、ecdsa — 含已加密的）。每次工作階段啟動時，金鑰會載入此設定專屬的 bromure ssh-agent；密語儲存在 macOS 鑰匙圈中。";
"Private mode" = "私密模式";
"Quay (quay.io)" = "Quay (quay.io)";
"Real value" = "真實值";
"Refresh" = "重新整理";
"Remove this credential" = "移除此認證";
"Remove this token rule" = "移除此權杖規則";
"Server" = "伺服器";
"Session trace" = "工作階段追蹤";
"Sessions running under this profile normally stream metadata (tools, files, commands, token usage) to your workspace. Turn this on to keep this profile's activity local — neither the title-bar indicator nor the admin's session list will see anything from this profile. The local trace inspector is unaffected." = "在此設定下執行的工作階段通常會將後設資料（工具、檔案、指令、權杖用量）串流到您的工作區。啟用此項可將此設定的活動保留在本機 — 標題列指示器與管理員的工作階段清單皆無法看到此設定的任何資料。本機追蹤檢查器不受影響。";
"Storage controls only apply to real profiles. They appear in each profile's editor when you create or edit one." = "儲存控制僅對實際的設定有效。當您建立或編輯設定時，它們會出現在該設定的編輯器中。";
"Stripe sandbox" = "Stripe 沙盒";
"The VM gets a LAN-routable IP via DHCP on the chosen interface." = "虛擬機透過所選介面的 DHCP 取得一個可在區域網路內路由的 IP 位址。";
"Username" = "使用者名稱";
"VM sits behind NAT. Egress works; nothing on your LAN can reach it." = "虛擬機位於 NAT 之後。對外連線可用；區域網路內的其他裝置無法存取它。";
"Your Name" = "您的姓名";
"real secret — stays on macOS" = "真實密鑰 — 僅保留在 macOS 上";

/* Preferences — Automation pane */
"Automation" = "自動化";
"Automation API & MCP server" = "自動化 API 與 MCP 伺服器";
"Bromure AC exposes an HTTP API on the loopback interface that lets external tools manage profiles and sessions. The bundled `bromure-ac mcp` subcommand wraps the same surface for AI agents (Claude Code, Claude Desktop). These settings apply app-wide." = "Bromure AC 於回送介面上公開 HTTP API，讓外部工具可管理設定與工作階段。隨附的 `bromure-ac mcp` 子指令為 AI 代理（Claude Code、Claude Desktop）包裝同一介面。這些設定會套用到整個 App。";
"Enable automation server" = "啟用自動化伺服器";
"Listening on %@:%@. Toggling this off stops the server immediately; the MCP subcommand will no longer reach the app." = "正在 %@:%@ 接聽。關閉此項會立即停止伺服器，MCP 子指令將無法與 App 連線。";
"Off — the HTTP API and the MCP subcommand are unavailable." = "已關閉 — HTTP API 與 MCP 子指令皆無法使用。";
"Port" = "連接埠";
"(default: 9223)" = "（預設：9223）";
"Bind address" = "繫結位址";
"Non-loopback bind exposes the API to the network. The MCP server has no auth." = "非回送位址繫結會將 API 暴露至網路。MCP 伺服器沒有任何驗證。";
"Port and bind address take effect the next time the server starts. Toggling the switch off and on applies them now." = "連接埠與繫結位址會在伺服器下次啟動時生效。將開關關閉再開啟即可立即套用。";
"MCP client configuration" = "MCP 用戶端設定";
"Add this to `~/.config/claude-code/.mcp.json` (or your MCP client's equivalent):" = "請將此加入到 `~/.config/claude-code/.mcp.json`（或您 MCP 用戶端的對應檔案）：";

/* Reboot */
"Reboot “%@”?" = "重新啟動「%@」？";
"Soft reboot" = "軟重啟";
"Hard reboot" = "硬重啟";
"Soft reboot gracefully halts the VM (filesystems flush, services stop) and boots a fresh one in this window. Hard reboot tears down the VM immediately and starts a fresh one." = "軟重啟會正常關閉虛擬機（清空檔案系統、停止服務），並在此視窗中啟動一個全新的虛擬機。硬重啟會立即銷毀虛擬機並啟動一個新的。";
